Maintainer: Yunyi Cheng <yunyi.cheng@outlook.com>
Description: A pipeline for the design of mutagenizing oligonucleotides required for Tile Region Exchange Mutagenesis (T-Rex), which is a crucial step for deep mutation scanning (DMS), by harnessing data-optimized assembly design (DAD).
